1. *Vojnik* je spreman da izvrši svoje dužnosti. (The soldier is ready to fulfil his duties.)

2. *Vojnik* će biti nagrađen za svoje herojske dela. (The soldier will be rewarded for his heroic deeds.)

3. *Vojnicima* je bilo teško da se prilagode novim uslovima. (The soldiers had a hard time adjusting to the new conditions.)

4. On je postao *vojnik* još pre nekoliko godina. (He became a soldier several years ago.)

5. *Vojnici* su bili odani svojoj zemlji. (The soldiers were loyal to their country.)